    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>remaining garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cider vinegar</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) in a bowl</p><p>Season with a generous crack of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
