      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 20 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and make a well[s] in the vegetables, then crack your <strong>egg[s] </strong>into the well[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 3-4 min or until the egg is done to your liking – this is your <strong>smoky chorizo & egg traybake</strong></p>",
