    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky chorizo & egg traybake</strong> on plates with your <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Dollop over the <strong>garlic mayo</strong> and drizzle the <strong>remaining cider vinegar</strong> over the salad with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
